flowchart TD
    Start([App Starts]) --> LoadDB[Load history rows from SQLite]
    LoadDB --> Rebuild[Reconstruct Doubly Linked List]
    Rebuild --> RestoreCurrent[Restore current pointer]
    RestoreCurrent --> UI[Render Streamlit UI]

    UI --> Action{User Action}

    Action -->|Visit URL| Validate{Valid URL?}
    Validate -->|No| ShowError1[Show InvalidURLError]
    Validate -->|Yes| Dup{Same as current?}
    Dup -->|Yes| ShowError2[Show DuplicateVisitError]
    Dup -->|No| HasForward{current.next exists?}
    HasForward -->|Yes| DeleteFwd[Delete forward history]
    HasForward -->|No| Insert[Insert new node after current]
    DeleteFwd --> Insert
    Insert --> Sync1[Sync to SQLite]
    Sync1 --> UI

    Action -->|Back| CheckPrev{current.prev exists?}
    CheckPrev -->|No| NullNav1[No-op: null navigation]
    CheckPrev -->|Yes| MoveBack[current = current.prev]
    MoveBack --> Sync2[Sync to SQLite]
    Sync2 --> UI
    NullNav1 --> UI

    Action -->|Forward| CheckNext{current.next exists?}
    CheckNext -->|No| NullNav2[No-op: null navigation]
    CheckNext -->|Yes| MoveFwd[current = current.next]
    MoveFwd --> Sync3[Sync to SQLite]
    Sync3 --> UI
    NullNav2 --> UI

    Action -->|Search| Traverse[Traverse head to tail, match keyword]
    Traverse --> ShowResults[Display matching nodes]
    ShowResults --> UI

    Action -->|Delete Selected| Unlink[Re-link prev/next neighbours]
    Unlink --> AdjustCurrent[Adjust current pointer if needed]
    AdjustCurrent --> Sync4[Sync to SQLite]
    Sync4 --> UI

    Action -->|Clear History| Reset[Reset head, tail, current to None]
    Reset --> ClearDB[Delete all rows from SQLite]
    ClearDB --> UI

    ShowError1 --> UI
    ShowError2 --> UI
